Thomas Callaway (actor and interior designer) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Callaway_(actor_and_interior_designer) 0 Thomas Callaway is a retired American actor, who last performed on screen in 1995. He was also credited as Tom Callaway. He has since become a successful interior designer in the Greater Los Angeles Area.
